{"tid":2490771,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆就快會監管網絡、媒體，房屋台ching 點睇","createTime":"2021-04-16T00:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:51:08.000Z","uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ee911db30b8964878ce704d9b5ccd78a349b38","tid":2490771,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:41:55.000Z","msg":"到時冇晒淡淡唱淡，我諗樓市會進入亢奮狀態，唔止GOGOGO 咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">林鄭月娥表示，特區政府會依照香港國安法第9條，採取必要措施，加強宣傳、指導、監督和管理學校、社會團體、媒體、網絡等對國家安全事宜的處理。</span><br />\n<br />\n有政界中人指，港澳辦副主任張曉明上月亦曾提到，在某些領域如教育，確實需要注意一些正本清源、撥亂反正的工作，相信中央會在逐個界別做工作，將來可能有更多「監管」工作出台，媒體、教育自然「走唔甩」。"},{"pid":"fdd34eaf8690e05280446ab18c773de960ae1a6c","tid":2490771,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />drop to zero"},{"pid":"39b5b688614e16c78b9fc0da36ec89250363ae7e","tid":2490771,"uid":251102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"h